title: Jennifer Garner, Ben Affleck not expecting a baby
text:
Estranged Hollywood couple Jennifer Garner and Ben Affleck are not currently expecting a baby together despite a tabloid report.
READ: Jennifer Garner makes 1st red-carpet appearance after Ben Affleck split
A report published by hollywoodlife.com claimed that the divorced couple is expecting a baby, saying "there may be a little bun in the oven".
Responding to the report, a representative for the 43-year-old actress denied the rumours.
"It's not true," the representative was Quote: d as saying by Gossip Cop magazine, reports aceshowbiz.com.
Garner isn't currently pregnant with her fourth baby and they are not going to dismiss their divorce paper.
The two announced their divorce in late June after 10 years of marriage.
Following their divorce announcement, the two were said to continue on living in the same property here, though in separate houses, to co-parent their children.
